{"tid":1201343,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"舊灣仔警署《機動部隊》海報被吹翻　警封路移除","createTime":"2019-06-11T04:10:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-11T04:17:12.000Z","uid":6497,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"be72649fc427f5dab63b9bff75d27569a891caef","tid":1201343,"uid":6497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T04:10:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20190611/s00001/ad6d56aec511ac8723bf1321aa6fc91e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20190611%2Fs00001%2Fad6d56aec511ac8723bf1321aa6fc91e.jpg&h=9682416d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20190611/s00001/ad6d6bc8fb1af00b95cbb7735f49f557.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20190611%2Fs00001%2Fad6d6bc8fb1af00b95cbb7735f49f557.jpg&h=2956ea0a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20190611/s00001/ad6d8214c908318fd83cc6b20de95539.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20190611%2Fs00001%2Fad6d8214c908318fd83cc6b20de95539.jpg&h=1cbfaa6a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n早上9時30分，舊灣仔警署外懸掛的一幅警隊宣傳海報，其中一條繩索疑被強風吹毀，海報隨即吹翻，一度掛上附近燈柱上，另一幅海報則墜落地面。警方到場封閉對出告士打道一段路面，通知消防處派員到場協助移除。<br />\n<br />\n涉事海報為宣傳近月警務處與電視台合作拍攝的劇集《機動部隊》，慶祝警隊成立175周年。"},{"pid":"21180ecdd0abde5b13c11530196814a71a57370b","tid":1201343,"uid":155818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T04:10:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"578c81337e63c22d728f873c0a7456b42ab7ea7e","tid":1201343,"uid":62257,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T04:11:43.000Z","msg":"神蹟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a38b24b4a6d0f38b68636d18daadac74e3722fc","tid":1201343,"uid":29080,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T04:11:53.000Z","msg":"不好的兆頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/